---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Accessibility Statement">
  <main id="main" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 prose">
    <h1>Accessibility Statement</h1>
    <p>We are committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We are continually improving the user experience for everyone and applying the relevant accessibility standards.</p>
    <h2>Conformance status</h2>
    <p>This site aims to conform to <strong>WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong>.</p>
    <h2>Feedback</h2>
    <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:dcraderdev@gmail.com">dcraderdev@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    <h2>Compatibility</h2>
    <p>Designed to be compatible with recent browsers and screen readers.</p>
    <p><em>Last updated: 2026-05-17</em></p>
  </main>
</Layout>
